&lt;li&gt;Take initiative and ownership of high-level work, negotiating and driving alignment with product architects, managers, and other key stakeholders across multiple disciplines.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and drive to completion complex system DoEs spanning several engineering disciplines including EE, ME, FW, and SW.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
